{"tid":1822843,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"<爭取功能組別議席> - 呼籲飲食界人士做功能界別選民 – 食黃店做文宣","createTime":"2020-01-13T08:03:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-24T14:02:35.000Z","uid":22121,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"3f596021afdc64552b260ed9a3f70a122a14b28c","tid":1822843,"uid":22121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T08:03:53.000Z","msg":"2020年立法會選舉行預定9月就會舉行<br />\n<br />\n而功能組別選民截止日期係 4月2號<br />\n<br />\n飲食界組別係我哋好有可以大幅度增加選民嘅議席<br />\n<br />\n我哋唔好放過呢個機會呀<br />\n<br />\n各個飲食界同路人快啲登記做飲食界組別選民啦<br />\n<br />\n各位食黃店嘅手足都可以做下文宣，呼籲下老細登記做選民，喺呢個不公平嘅制席下爭取表達自己嘅意見。<br />\n<br />\n已經有手足幫緊手，感謝手足，TG link 喺下面<br />\n<br />\nFrom tg channel 轉發<br />\n緊急召集之Telegram頻道<br />\n@cateringvote<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/cateringvote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fcateringvote&d=EP%2BJfZZVzGvO4DQPpGaiyNUsrLV3ynd9sCeqRx8pZcg%3D&h=ad5c7f92\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/cateringvote</a><br />\n<br />\n----------------<br />\n相關文宣及功能界別報名表格<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2PY66C9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2PY66C9&d=EP%2BJfZZVzGvO4DQPpGaiyNUsrLV3ynd9sCeqRx8pZcg%3D&h=b0c711ec\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2PY66C9</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%9C%89%E9%97%9C2020%E7%AB%8B%E6%B3%95%E6%9C%83%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%E7%B5%84%E5%88%A5%E9%81%B8%E8%88%89/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%259C%2589%25E9%2597%259C2020%25E7%25AB%258B%25E6%25B3%2595%25E6%259C%2583%25E5%258A%259F%25E8%2583%25BD%25E7%25B5%2584%25E5%2588%25A5%25E9%2581%25B8%25E8%2588%2589%2F&d=EP%2BJfZZVzGvO4DQPpGaiyNUsrLV3ynd9sCeqRx8pZcg%3D&h=ca7f0592\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%259C%2589%25E9%2597%259C2020%25E7%25AB%258B%25E6%25B3%2595%25E6%259C%2583%25E5%258A%259F%25E8%2583%25BD%25E7%25B5%2584%25E5%2588%25A5%25E9%2